# PesoSense Assets

Place the following assets in their respective subdirectories:

## assets/images/
- `logo.png` — App logo
- `onboarding_1.png` — Welcome illustration
- `onboarding_2.png` — Vision profile illustration
- `bill_*.png` — Denomination reference images
- `coin_*.png` — Coin reference images

## assets/lottie/
- `scanning.json` — Lottie animation for scanning state
- `processing.json` — Lottie animation for processing state
- `success.json` — Lottie animation for successful detection

## assets/audio/
- Audio files for TTS fallback (if flutter_tts is unavailable)
